overview: Sydney is a traditional masseuse and shes losing business. Its time for her to step up her game. Enter sexy zen-master Drew who shows her erotic alternative therapies that keep her and her clients coming back for more! Stunning Aidra Fox is the ready and willing masseuse, vivacious Marley Brinx, exotic Kira Noir and Logan Pierce are clients, Seth Gamble is Sydneys apt employee and the one and only James Deen is Drew.
title: The Masseuse 10
